{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A sort of intermediary to run this business, or to confiscate, or to liquidate it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was enough food because we had access to the, like I said-- we had access to the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I would steal leather from the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or I would bring this father-- the owner's father was working with me in the warehouse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a real old-timer, and he hated the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he used to confide in me, and I would go and get stuff for him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would buy tobacco for him on the black market.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would give me leathers, soles, cut soles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or even the top leather, or made shoes, and I would take this to the black market to sell it and buy whatever he wanted.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wanted liquor or-- the biggest thing he wanted was pipe tobacco.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was his biggest desire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was making them money and being able to buy bread, and we lived from that very well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father worked as well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He worked in a tailor shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What were you living conditions like in Srodula?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very-- we had one room in which the four of us lived in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two beds, one on either side of the room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was the table between the two beds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was our living room, our dining room, and our bedroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we had commode against one wall, and a wash stand, and a curtain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you looked after him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think there were hospitals at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just brought the doctor in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The doctors were still around with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know what medication there was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But if you were very sick, you died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was as simple as that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
